---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../../../components/ui/Section.astro';
import Row from '../../../components/ui/Row.astro';
import Col from '../../../components/ui/Col.astro';
import Button from '../../../components/ui/Button.astro';
import Feature from '../../../components/ui/Feature.astro';
import List from '../../../components/ui/List.astro';
import MetricBar from '../../../components/ui/MetricBar.astro';
import { t } from '../../../i18n';

const i18n = t('en');
import CtaBanner from '../../../components/CtaBanner.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title={`${i18n.services.teamPerformance.name} - ${i18n.site.title}`} description={i18n.site.descriptions.teamPerformance} seoType="service">

  <Section padding="both" classes="bg-neutral-50">
    <Row>
      <Col span="2" />
      <Col span="8" align="center">
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary-500">Execution</p>
        <h1 class="mb-4 font-headings text-4xl font-black tracking-tight text-neutral-900 lg:text-5xl">{i18n.services.teamPerformance.name}</h1>
        <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-lg text-neutral-500">{i18n.services.teamPerformance.tagline}</p>
      </Col>
      <Col span="2" />
    </Row>
  </Section>

  <Section padding="both">
    <Row>
      <Col span="2" />
      <Col span="8">
        <h2 class="mb-6 font-headings text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900">The problem you are facing</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-neutral-600">
          <p>Your sprints end with unfinished stories. Production incidents and regressions are piling up. Technical debt grows faster than it shrinks. Your best developers are starting to leave.</p>
          <p>Your teams are experimenting with AI on their own: Copilot here, ChatGPT there, without a common method, without measuring the real gains. Legacy documentation is obsolete or non-existent. The quality vs velocity trade-off is never resolved.</p>
          <p>You have tried adding tools, changing frameworks, hiring more. But the problem is not technical: it is the way your team specifies, develops, tests and delivers that is the real lever.</p>
        </div>
      </Col>
      <Col span="2" />
    </Row>
  </Section>

  <Section padding="both" classes="bg-neutral-50">
    <Row>
      <Col span="2" />
      <Col span="8">
        <h2 class="mb-6 font-headings text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900">My approach: Coach-Craft</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 text-neutral-600">I measure before acting. My approach relies on DORA metrics, process observation, and individual interviews to build a factual diagnostic. Then I coach your team on real sprints, not in a training room.</p>
        <p class="mb-8 text-neutral-600">The Coach-Craft method follows 4 steps: <strong>demonstration</strong> (I show on your real projects), <strong>guided practice</strong> (pair programming, pedagogical reviews), <strong>progressive autonomy</strong> (tech leads take over), <strong>lasting anchoring</strong> (internal champions trained to sustain). The goal is autonomy, not dependency.</p>
        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
          <Feature icon="heroicons:magnifying-glass" title="Phase 1: Diagnostic (1-2 weeks)" type="side-icon" iconStyle="square" align="left">
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Individual interviews, DORA metrics, process observation, ecosystem mapping (tools, workflows, AI initiatives, interdependencies). Quick win identification and sector benchmarking.</p>
          </Feature>
          <Feature icon="heroicons:bolt" title="Phase 2: Embedded coaching (4-8 weeks)" type="side-icon" iconStyle="square" align="left">
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Pair programming on real projects. Pedagogical code reviews. Introduction of Specification-Driven Development (SDD): specify first, generate next. CI/CD setup, quality gates, test coverage.</p>
          </Feature>
          <Feature icon="heroicons:arrow-trending-up" title="Phase 3: Autonomy (4 weeks)" type="side-icon" iconStyle="square" align="left">
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Tech leads take over. Final KPI measurement. Complete practice transfer. Documentation of validated workflows. The team continues without me.</p>
          </Feature>
          <Feature icon="heroicons:cpu-chip" title="SDD methodology" type="side-icon" iconStyle="square" align="left">
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Specification-Driven Development: AI is an executor that transforms specifications into code, not an oracle that guesses intent. Acceleration: 5-10 user stories/day, delivery cycle -30%, test coverage 80%+.</p>
          </Feature>
        </div>
      </Col>
      <Col span="2" />
    </Row>
  </Section>

  <Section padding="both">
    <Row>
      <Col span="2" />
      <Col span="8">
        <h2 class="mb-6 font-headings text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Philosophy: "Code is Cattle, Context is King"</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 text-neutral-600">AI can generate code faster and cheaper than any human. The value is no longer in the code itself: it is a <strong>regenerable derivative</strong>. Your true assets are your <strong>specifications</strong> and your <strong>tests</strong>. If your specs are precise and your tests complete, you can regenerate your entire codebase on demand.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
          <div class="flex w-full max-w-lg items-center justify-center rounded-t-lg bg-secondary-600 px-6 py-4 text-center">
            <div>
              <p class="font-headings text-lg font-bold text-white">Specifications</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-secondary-100">Primary asset. The "what" and the "why". Source of truth.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex w-full max-w-sm items-center justify-center bg-secondary-400 px-6 py-4 text-center">
            <div>
              <p class="font-headings text-lg font-bold text-white">Tests</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-secondary-50">Primary asset. The safety net. Guarantees the "how".</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex w-full max-w-xs items-center justify-center rounded-b-lg bg-neutral-200 px-6 py-4 text-center">
            <div>
              <p class="font-headings text-lg font-bold text-neutral-400">Code</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">Regenerable derivative. An artefact, no longer an asset.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Col>
      <Col span="2" />
    </Row>
  </Section>

  <Section padding="both" classes="bg-neutral-50">
    <Row>
      <Col span="2" />
      <Col span="8">
        <h2 class="mb-6 font-headings text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900">The 4 pain points every CIO knows</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 text-neutral-600">Every transformation engagement starts from the same ground realities, validated with dozens of CIOs in finance, insurance and public sector:</p>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-lg border-l-4 border-secondary-400 bg-white p-5">
            <h3 class="mb-1 font-headings font-bold text-neutral-900">1. Understand</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">"What does this system actually do, in its entirety?" Not a single forgotten connection, function or stored procedure.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border-l-4 border-secondary-400 bg-white p-5">
            <h3 class="mb-1 font-headings font-bold text-neutral-900">2. Document</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">"How do we capture knowledge before it retires?" No more tribal knowledge walking out the door.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border-l-4 border-secondary-400 bg-white p-5">
            <h3 class="mb-1 font-headings font-bold text-neutral-900">3. Secure</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">"Where are the vulnerabilities hiding in this legacy?" Every change is a risk as long as the perimeter is not controlled.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border-l-4 border-secondary-400 bg-white p-5">
            <h3 class="mb-1 font-headings font-bold text-neutral-900">4. Evolve</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">"How do we evolve without breaking everything?" The Onion Model approach: modernise from outside in, layer by layer.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Col>
      <Col span="2" />
    </Row>
  </Section>

  <Section padding="both">
    <Row>
      <Col span="2" />
      <Col span="8">
        <h2 class="mb-6 font-headings text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Measured results from real missions</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-secondary-50 p-4 text-center">
            <p class="font-headings text-2xl font-black text-secondary-600">5% → 65%</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">test coverage</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-secondary-50 p-4 text-center">
            <p class="font-headings text-2xl font-black text-secondary-600">-70%</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">prod regressions</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-secondary-50 p-4 text-center">
            <p class="font-headings text-2xl font-black text-secondary-600">-96%</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">lead time (2d → 2h)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-secondary-50 p-4 text-center">
            <p class="font-headings text-2xl font-black text-secondary-600">-73%</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">technical debt</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 p-6">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary-500">Measured progression (6 months)</p>
          <MetricBar label="Test coverage" before="5%" after="65%" beforeValue={5} afterValue={65} />
          <MetricBar label="Production regressions" before="10/month" after="3/month" beforeValue={100} afterValue={30} inverted />
          <MetricBar label="Delivery lead time" before="2 days" after="2 hours" beforeValue={100} afterValue={4} inverted />
          <MetricBar label="Technical debt (SonarQube)" before="45 days" after="12 days" beforeValue={100} afterValue={27} inverted />
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-neutral-400">Results measured on a 6-month technical coaching mission (digital agency, 30 developers).</p>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-neutral-50 p-4 text-center">
            <p class="font-headings text-2xl font-black text-neutral-700">x4-x5</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">productivity with SDD</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-neutral-50 p-4 text-center">
            <p class="font-headings text-2xl font-black text-neutral-700">3-5 days</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">time to first sprint (vs 3-5 weeks)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg bg-neutral-50 p-4 text-center">
            <p class="font-headings text-2xl font-black text-neutral-700">80%+</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">target test coverage</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Col>
      <Col span="2" />
    </Row>
  </Section>

  <Section padding="both" classes="bg-neutral-50">
    <Row>
      <Col span="2" />
      <Col span="8">
        <h2 class="mb-8 font-headings text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Engagement formats</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-lg border-2 border-secondary-200 bg-secondary-50/30 p-6">
            <p class="mb-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary-500">Entry point</p>
            <h3 class="mb-2 font-headings text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Flash diagnostic</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-neutral-500">Ecosystem mapping, maturity benchmarks, 5-8 concrete recommendations, costed roadmap at 3, 6 and 12 months. The CTO leaves with the arguments to invest.</p>
            <List type="checklist" listItems={[
              { listItem: "3-5 days (including 1 day on site)" },
              { listItem: "Deliverable: report + benchmarks + roadmap" },
              { listItem: "CHF 5,500 - 9,000" },
            ]} />
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 p-6">
            <p class="mb-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400">Transformation</p>
            <h3 class="mb-2 font-headings text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900">12-week embedded coaching</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-neutral-500">Coaching on real sprints. Pair programming, code reviews, SDD, CI/CD, quality gates. Measurable DORA metrics from month 3.</p>
            <List type="checklist" listItems={[
              { listItem: "12 weeks (3d/wk then 2d/wk)" },
              { listItem: "CHF 45,000 - 55,000" },
              { listItem: "KPIs measured: quality, velocity, efficiency" },
            ]} />
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 p-6">
            <p class="mb-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400">One-off</p>
            <h3 class="mb-2 font-headings text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Culture workshop</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-neutral-500">3 half-days on a specific topic (code review, incident management, testing, AI for developers). Before/after survey.</p>
            <List type="checklist" listItems={[
              { listItem: "5-6 days preparation + facilitation" },
              { listItem: "CHF 9,500 - 11,000" },
            ]} />
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 p-6">
            <p class="mb-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400">One-off</p>
            <h3 class="mb-2 font-headings text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Leadership offsite</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-neutral-500">Full day facilitation for the technical leadership team. Vision, priorities, alignment, action plan.</p>
            <List type="checklist" listItems={[
              { listItem: "3 days (preparation + facilitation)" },
              { listItem: "CHF 5,500" },
            ]} />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 p-6">
          <p class="mb-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary-500">New</p>
          <h3 class="mb-2 font-headings text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900">SDLC Assessment</h3>
          <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-neutral-500">Complete mapping of your development cycle (specifications, design, build, test, deploy, operate). Identification of AI accelerations per stage. Transformation roadmap with priorities and a sellable first step.</p>
          <List type="checklist" listItems={[
            { listItem: "2-3 weeks" },
            { listItem: "Deliverable: SDLC roadmap + priority use cases" },
            { listItem: "CHF 15,000 - 25,000" },
          ]} />
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-neutral-400">Full journey (diagnostic + 12-week coaching + workshops + annual offsite): CHF 40,000 - 55,000 in the first year.</p>
      </Col>
      <Col span="2" />
    </Row>
  </Section>

  <Section padding="both">
    <Row>
      <Col span="2" />
      <Col span="8">
        <h2 class="mb-6 font-headings text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900">Who is it for</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 font-headings text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900">CTO / VP Engineering</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Who know their team can do better but cannot identify the concrete levers. Need a factual diagnostic and coaching on real sprints.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 font-headings text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900">Teams adopting AI</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Who are experimenting with Copilot or ChatGPT individually and need a common method (SDD) for AI to actually accelerate delivery.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 font-headings text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900">Growing scale-ups</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Whose artisanal processes no longer hold at scale and who need to professionalise their engineering without losing agility.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 font-headings text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900">Post-acquisition / merger</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Who need to align technical teams from different cultures, harmonise practices and tools.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Col>
      <Col span="2" />
    </Row>
  </Section>
  <CtaBanner lang="en" />

</BaseLayout>
